data.title: Joan Bennett - Autographed Signed Photograph
data.meta_description: Joan Bennett - Autographed Signed Photograph  - Item 76024. Color 11x14 publicity photograph of Joan Bennett looking over her shoulder holding her hat.Photograph signed: 'All good wishes/Joan Bennett'. Color, 11x14. Veteran actress Joan Bennett played Madame Blanc in the film about witchcraft at the Tans Academy in Germany. Shop for  Joan Bennett related autographs, signed photographs, historical documents and manuscripts from the world's largest collection. Every purchase includes our industry recognized COA. Worldwide shipping available.
